  "detailed_description": "<h1>Play New Game Demo!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/e9fe09ea36d77aec972e0223cf404937.avif?t=1772327714\" width=600 height=280 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mars needs<i><strong> </strong></i><strong>YOU!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HOW CAN YOU HELP IT?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Step 1: Mine</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources from your mining machine and explore the various terrains it brings to you</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/574d712bd3e3f9e661a81e0243178ae4.poster.avif?t=1772327714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/574d712bd3e3f9e661a81e0243178ae4.webm?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/574d712bd3e3f9e661a81e0243178ae4.mp4?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Step 2: Build</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create robust machines of destruction to beat the robots attacking your home using materials and weapons you find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >use diffrent weapons to counter diffrent enemies you encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/aa83671710c8d13852d14032e5b52609.poster.avif?t=1772327714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/aa83671710c8d13852d14032e5b52609.webm?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/aa83671710c8d13852d14032e5b52609.mp4?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Step 3: Defend</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab arms and blast away at the waves of enemies using bullets, rockets, explosives, and everything in between</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/450bd491173673ac505ac78fe2369bcb.poster.avif?t=1772327714\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/450bd491173673ac505ac78fe2369bcb.webm?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/450bd491173673ac505ac78fe2369bcb.mp4?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >tons of items  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >mine materials from your mine</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >buy items from the shop with the materials you mine</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >build turrets with items you buy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >protect your core from waves of enemeis</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >arm yourself with weapons to shoot down enemies yourself</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/89fe89dedb93966431e0a2d81a0746e8.poster.avif?t=1772327714\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/89fe89dedb93966431e0a2d81a0746e8.webm?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144030/extras/89fe89dedb93966431e0a2d81a0746e8.mp4?t=1772327714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mars needs <strong><i>YOU!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>ENLIST NOW!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(by wishlisting)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
